{"source_url": "https://www.boomlive.in/entertainment/april-fools-day-roundup-lays-jalebi-flavor-salman-khan-marriage-shashi-tharoor-child-actor-twitter-edit-17382", "article_heading": "Lays Jalebi Flavor, Salman Khan Getting Married: Did You Get April Fooled?", "short_context": "From Lays introducing a jalebi flavor to Twitter announcing an edit button feature, here are some April Fools' jokes you might have fallen for.", "short_into": "Come April, and every year brands try to out do each other with their Fools Day pranks. This year was no different - with Jalebi flavoured chips to Twitter finally launching an edit button.", "author": "Anmol Alphonso", "date": "2 April 2022 2:13 PM GMT", "image_set1": ["https://www.boomlive.in/h-upload/2022/04/02/973866-untitled-design-47.webp"], "image_set2": ["https://www.boomlive.in/h-upload/2022/04/02/973867-itapril.webp", "https://www.boomlive.in/h-upload/2022/04/03/973869-screenshot20220403-105209twitter.webp"]}
{"source_url": "https://www.boomlive.in/fact-check/viral-video-muslim-shopkeeper-shortchanging-customers-fact-check-fake-news-17357", "article_heading": "Scripted Video Of Fruit Seller Cheating Customers Shared With Communal Spin", "short_context": "BOOM found that the viral video is a scripted act created by a content creator.", "short_into": "A scripted video of a fruit vendor duping customers is being shared on social media with a fake and communal caption claiming that the fruit seller is a Muslim.", "author": "Sumit Usha", "date": "31 March 2022 10:58 AM GMT", "image_set1": ["https://www.boomlive.in/h-upload/2022/03/31/973726--012.webp"], "image_set2": []}
{"source_url": "https://www.boomlive.in/fast-check/fake-news-cropped-video-arvind-kejriwal-gujarat-threatening-gujaratis-aam-aadmi-party-bharatiya-janata-party-amit-shah-factcheck-17360", "article_heading": "Cropped Video Revived Falsely Claiming Arvind Kejriwal Threatened Gujaratis", "short_context": "BOOM found that in the original 2016 video, Arvind Kejriwal is referring to Amit Shah and criticising him for police action against protesters in Gujarat.", "short_into": "Video shows Delhi Chief Minister Arvind Kejriwal say, \"People of Gujarat, if you protest against me, then you shall be crushed, what you can do about that, go do.\"   (Original text - \u0905\u0917\u0930 \u092e\u0947\u0930\u0947 \u0916\u093f\u0932\u093e\u092b \u0906\u0935\u093e\u091c \u0915\u0930\u094b\u0917\u0947 \u0924\u094b \u092e\u0948\u0902 \u0915\u0941\u091a\u0932 \u0926\u0942\u0902\u0917\u093e - \u0905\u0930\u0935\u093f\u0902\u0926 \u0915\u0947\u091c\u0930\u0940\u0935\u093e\u0932)", "author": "Anmol Alphonso", "date": "31 March 2022 11:43 AM GMT", "image_set1": ["https://www.boomlive.in/h-upload/2022/03/31/973718-ak-edited-speech.webp"], "image_set2": []}
{"source_url": "https://www.boomlive.in/fact-check/politics/viral-video-prime-minister-narendra-modi-speech-ballot-paper-cropped-old-video-social-media-17362", "article_heading": "Cropped Video Falsely Shared As Modi Questioning EVMs Before Becoming PM", "short_context": "BOOM found that the video is cropped and is being shared out of context.", "short_into": "A cropped video of Prime Minister Narendra Modi is being shared on social media with a false claim that Modi expressed doubts over Electronic Voting Machines (EVM) before becoming the prime minister.", "author": "Srijit Das", "date": "31 March 2022 12:29 PM GMT", "image_set1": ["https://www.boomlive.in/h-upload/2022/03/31/973700-modi-evm-02.webp"], "image_set2": []}
{"source_url": "https://www.boomlive.in/fact-check/fact-check-pfizer-oscars-chris-rock-will-smith-slap-alopecia-pr-stunt-conspiracy-17369", "article_heading": "Did Pfizer Plan Oscar Slap To Promote Alopecia Drug? A FactCheck", "short_context": "A Pfizer spokesperson rubbished the allegation and said that the company had no role to play in the slapping incident that occurred between Will Smith and Chris Rock", "short_into": "Social media posts claiming Pfizer orchestrated Will Smith slapping Chris Rock at the Oscars to promote its drug against alopecia, are false with the drugmaker rubbishing the same.", "author": "Shachi Sutaria", "date": "1 April 2022 9:11 AM GMT", "image_set1": ["https://www.boomlive.in/h-upload/2022/03/31/973747-pfizer-03.webp"], "image_set2": []}
{"source_url": "https://www.boomlive.in/fast-check/swami-nimai-das-iftar-to-muslims-bangladesh-iskcon-temple-killed-in-riots-fake-news-fact-check-17371", "article_heading": "Photo From West Bengal Falsely Shared As ISKCON Priest Killed In Bangladesh", "short_context": "BOOM contacted ISKCON Mayapur, West Bengal last year and confirmed that the man seen in the viral photo was not killed in Bangladesh.", "short_into": "A photo of an ISKCON devotee in Mayapur, West Bengal serving food to Muslim men during Ramzan has been revived with a false claim that it shows a Hindu priest who was killed by a Muslim mob in Bangladesh.  Bangladesh was rocked by communal violence during Durga Puja in October 2021, which claimed 11 lives across the country that time. ", "author": "Sk Badiruddin", "date": "1 April 2022 9:27 AM GMT", "image_set1": ["https://www.boomlive.in/h-upload/2022/04/01/973784-iskcon-devotee-killed.webp"], "image_set2": []}
{"source_url": "https://www.boomlive.in/fact-check/uttar-pradesh-chief-minister-yogi-adityanath-shah-rukh-khan-film-pathan-viral-video-17335", "article_heading": "Did Yogi Adityanath Urge People Not To Watch Shah Rukh Khan's 'Pathan'?", "short_context": "BOOM found that the viral video is from 2015 when Yogi Adityanath had slammed the Bollywood actor for a different reason.", "short_into": "An old video showing Uttar Pradesh Chief Minister Yogi Adityanath speaking about Bollywood actor Shah Rukh Khan is viral on social media with captions falsely claiming that the chief minister had advised people against watching the actor's upcoming film '", "author": "Sumit Usha", "date": "30 March 2022 11:20 AM GMT", "image_set1": ["https://www.boomlive.in/h-upload/2022/03/30/973581-srk-and-yogi-03.webp"], "image_set2": []}
{"source_url": "https://www.boomlive.in/fact-check/politics/viral-photo-bhagwant-mann-bike-stealing-punjab-police-holi-celebration-old-photo-social-media-17349", "article_heading": "No, This Photo Does Not Show Punjab CM Bhagwant Mann Caught Stealing A Bike", "short_context": "BOOM found that the old photo shows Mann celebrating Holi with his friends.", "short_into": "An old photograph of newly-elected Punjab Chief Minister Bhagwant Mann is being widely shared on social media with a false claim that the picture is from when Punjab Police nabbed Mann and three others for stealing a bike.", "author": "Srijit Das", "date": "31 March 2022 7:43 AM GMT", "image_set1": ["https://www.boomlive.in/h-upload/2022/03/31/973689-bhagwant-mann-01.webp"], "image_set2": []}
{"source_url": "https://www.boomlive.in/fact-check/politics/viral-photo-photoshopped-arvind-kejriwal-home-vandalised-gate-bjp-workers-the-kashmir-files-vivek-agnihotri-factcheck-17354", "article_heading": "Photo Of Arvind Kejriwal's Gate With 'The Kashmir Files' On It Is Not Real", "short_context": "BOOM found that while the gate in front of the CM's house was defaced with paint, the viral photo which includes text is digitally altered.", "short_into": "A photo showing the gate of Delhi Chief Minister Arvind Kejriwal's residence with red paint smeared on it and text that says 'The Kashmir Files, Is Not A Lie It's Horrifying Truth', is morphed with the text digitally added to the image.", "author": "Anmol Alphonso", "date": "31 March 2022 10:32 AM GMT", "image_set1": ["https://www.boomlive.in/h-upload/2022/03/31/973709-kashmir-file-03.webp"], "image_set2": []}
{"source_url": "https://www.boomlive.in/fast-check/bangladeshs-exorcism-video-revived-forced-conversion-hindu-muslim-in-west-bengal-17372", "article_heading": "Exorcism Video From Bangladesh Peddled As Forced Conversion In West Bengal", "short_context": "BOOM found that the video shows an exorcism ritual performed in Bangladesh and not a forced conversion of a Hindu woman in West Bengal as claimed.", "short_into": "A disturbing video of an exorcism performed in Bangladesh has resurfaced on Twitter with a false claim that it shows a Hindu woman being forcibly converted to Islam, in West Bengal. The distressing 16 seconds video shows a woman seated on the floor undergoing the ritual. A man (not seen in the in the frame) appears to threaten her with a knife. The video has been shared ", "author": "Sk Badiruddin", "date": "1 April 2022 10:04 AM GMT", "image_set1": ["https://www.boomlive.in/h-upload/2022/04/01/973798-excorcism-video-bengal.webp"], "image_set2": []}
{"source_url": "https://www.boomlive.in/fact-check/politics/fact-check-viral-video-tailor-muslim-hindu-woman-molestation-communal-spin-fake-news-youtube-awareness-video-17374", "article_heading": "Scripted Video Of Tailor Touching Woman Inappropriately Viral With Communal Claim", "short_context": "The video is a dramatised video created by a YouTube channel and not a real incident caught on CCTV camera.", "short_into": "A scripted video purporting to show a tailor inappropriately touch a woman while taking her measurements, is being shared online with false claims targeting Muslims and urging Hindu women to avoid small businesses run by Muslims. ", "author": "Runjay Kumar", "date": "1 April 2022 12:45 PM GMT", "image_set1": ["https://www.boomlive.in/h-upload/2022/04/01/973808-973731-muslim-tailor-01.webp"], "image_set2": []}
{"source_url": "https://www.boomlive.in/fact-check/politics/fake-news-shashi-tharoor-child-actor-black-and-white-photo-april-fools-day-prank-factcheck-17379", "article_heading": "Photo Of Shashi Tharoor As A Child Actor? No, It's An April 1st Joke!", "short_context": "Congress MP Shashi Tharoor clarified on Twitter that he went along with an April Fool's Day joke which identified him in an old black and white photo as a child actor in a Bollywood movie.", "short_into": "A black and white photo still from an old Bollywood movie was tweeted by film writer Vaibhav Vishal sarcastically identifying the child actor as Congress leader Shashi Tharoor. However, this friendly banter between the two on April Fools' Day led to several Twitter users falling for the joke as it was originally intended.", "author": "Anmol Alphonso", "date": "2 April 2022 10:19 AM GMT", "image_set1": ["https://www.boomlive.in/h-upload/2022/04/02/973857-untitled-design-46.webp"], "image_set2": []}
{"source_url": "https://www.boomlive.in/law/delhi-high-court-rana-ayyub-mumbai-airport-london-intimidation-of-journalists-enforcement-directorate-money-laundering-17368", "article_heading": "Delhi HC To Hear Rana Ayyub Plea On Monday, No Relief Yet", "short_context": "Journalist Rana Ayyub is slated to deliver a keynote address on the intimidation of journalists with ICFJ in London.", "short_into": "Journalist Rana Ayyub, who petitioned the Delhi High Court for permission to travel abroad, will miss delivering her keynote address in person on gender-based online violence against journalists with the International Centre for Journalists (ICFJ) at London. The Delhi High Court directed the Enforcement Directorate to file a status report on Monday.", "author": "Ritika Jain", "date": "1 April 2022 8:50 AM GMT", "image_set1": ["https://www.boomlive.in/h-upload/2022/04/01/973772-rana-ayyub.webp"], "image_set2": []}
{"source_url": "https://www.boomlive.in/law/supreme-court-one-rank-one-pension-armed-forces-ex-servicemen-defence-ministry-17172", "article_heading": "Supreme Court Upholds Centre's OROP Policy for Ex-Servicemen", "short_context": "OROP was meant to ensure uniform pension for retired servicemen of the same rank with the same length of service irrespective of their date of retirement.", "short_into": "The Supreme Court on Wednesday upheld the Centre's policy on the One Rank One Pension (OROP) for ex-military servicemen and found no fault in its implementation. The bench led by Justice DY Chandrachud said there was \"no legal mandate that same rank pensioners must be given the same pension.\"", "author": "Ritika Jain", "date": "16 March 2022 6:09 AM GMT", "image_set1": ["https://www.boomlive.in/h-upload/2022/03/16/972504-pension.webp"], "image_set2": []}
{"source_url": "https://www.boomlive.in/explainers/imran-khan-pakistan-no-confidence-motion-shebaz-sharif-next-prime-minister-khan-resign-17380", "article_heading": "Explained: Imran Khan's Leadership Hanging By A Thread In Pakistan", "short_context": "While Imran Khan addressed to the nation and expressed his defiance against resignation, his tenure as PM may cut short", "short_into": "A fiery Imran Khan addressed his nation on March 31, showcasing his defiance, appealing to his cricketing past and said that he would play to the \"last ball\" as he refused to resign. ", "author": "Mohammed Kudrati", "date": "2 April 2022 10:22 AM GMT", "image_set1": ["https://www.boomlive.in/h-upload/2022/04/02/973865-imran-khan-0fi.webp"], "image_set2": []}
