{"source_url": "https://www.boomlive.in/world/fake-news-japan-earthquake-fukushima-17324", "article_heading": "Misleading Post Claims Fukushima Nuclear Plant On Fire Following Japan Earthquake", "short_context": "The photo in the misleading post dates back to 2011, after the earthquake in Japan led to the eruption of gas storage tanks in Chiba Prefecture.", "short_into": "After a 7.3-magnitude earthquake hit eastern Japan, Korean-language social media posts viewed hundreds of thousands of times shared two images alongside a claim that a large fire broke out at the Fukushima Daiichi Nuclear Plant. This is misleading; the plant's Japanese operator said although a fire alarm went off on March 16, 2022, no fire or smoke was detected. The posts shared two images unrelated to the recent earthquake -- one shows a Japanese oil refinery following an earthquake in 2011, and the other relates to an attack on a Tokyo train in 2021.", "author": "AFP", "date": "29 March 2022 10:17 AM GMT", "image_set1": ["https://www.boomlive.in/h-upload/2022/03/29/973435-5a781d403bb6e778e6a7d6fcfb87dcb2.webp"], "image_set2": []}
{"source_url": "https://www.boomlive.in/world/fake-news-pakistan-imran-khan-17322", "article_heading": "This Photo Is Not From Imran Khan's No-Confidence Vote In Pakistan", "short_context": "The picture actually dates back to 2016 when Imran Khan had a meeting with KP Pervez Khattak and Siraj ul Haq on Kashmir.", "short_into": "After Pakistan Prime Minister Imran Khan was left scrambling to fight a no-confidence vote, a photo was shared hundreds of times on Facebook and Twitter alongside a claim it shows Khan meeting with the head of an Islamist party to shore up support. But the photo has been shared in a misleading context: it shows Khan's meeting with the leader of the Jamaat-e-Islami Pakistan party in 2016.", "author": "AFP", "date": "29 March 2022 10:17 AM GMT", "image_set1": ["https://www.boomlive.in/h-upload/2022/03/29/973499-pakistan-imran-khan-fake-news.webp"], "image_set2": []}
{"source_url": "https://www.boomlive.in/world/fake-news-indonesia-parliament-general-election-17344", "article_heading": "Misleading Post Claims Indonesian General Elections Have Been 'Officially Postponed'", "short_context": "The Indonesian lawmaker featuring in the video is actually seen to suggest postponement of general elections.", "short_into": "A video clip of an Indonesian politician speaking about upcoming elections has been viewed tens of thousands of times alongside a claim the country's parliament \"has officially postponed\" the polls. However, the claim is misleading; the video actually shows a lawmaker saying he had suggested the postponement. As of March 30, 2022, Indonesia's general elections are scheduled for February 14, 2024. Constitutional law experts have said it would be \"legally difficult\" to delay the elections without amending the constitution.", "author": "AFP", "date": "30 March 2022 12:17 PM GMT", "image_set1": ["https://www.boomlive.in/h-upload/2022/03/30/973640-indonesia-elections.webp"], "image_set2": []}
{"source_url": "https://www.boomlive.in/world/fake-news-ukraine-russia-palestine-israel-17318", "article_heading": "This Misleading Video Post Claims Ukrainian Defence Ministry Hit By Missiles", "short_context": "In reality, the tower featuring in the misleading video post is from Gaza after an Israeli strike in 2021.", "short_into": "Footage of a building collapsing after it was pummelled by missiles has been viewed thousands of times in social media posts that claim it shows a Russian strike on the Ukrainian defence ministry. However, the video shows Israeli strikes on a tower in Gaza in May 2021. ", "author": "AFP", "date": "29 March 2022 11:01 AM GMT", "image_set1": ["https://www.boomlive.in/h-upload/2022/03/29/973477-ukraine-russia-fake-news.webp"], "image_set2": []}
{"source_url": "https://www.boomlive.in/world/burj-khalifa-pakistan-prime-minister-imran-khan-confdence-vote-fact-check-17347", "article_heading": "Did Burj Khalifa Display Imran Khan's Message Ahead Of Confidence Vote?", "short_context": "The video, viewed more than 9,000 times, appears to show a clip of Khan speaking projected on the Burj Khalifa in Dubai.", "short_into": "Pakistan Tehreek-e-Insaaf (PTI), the party led by Imran Khan, lost majority in the lower house of Pakistan\u2019s Parliament after its main coalition partner Muttahida Qaumi Movement Pakistan (MQM-P) joined hands with the Opposition led by Pakistan People\u2019s Party (PPP)", "author": "AFP", "date": "31 March 2022 7:30 AM GMT", "image_set1": ["https://www.boomlive.in/h-upload/2022/03/30/973556-imran-fi.webp"], "image_set2": []}
{"source_url": "https://www.boomlive.in/world/chris-rock-will-smith-oscars-2022-slap-fact-check-17348", "article_heading": "Images From 2017 Peddled As Recent To Show Reactions To Oscar Slapgate", "short_context": "The images are from 2017, when \"La La Land\" was mistakenly announced instead of \"Moonlight\" as the winner of the Oscar for Best Picture.", "short_into": "Social media posts claim a collage of Hollywood celebrities' stunned faces shows their reactions to Will Smith hitting Chris Rock on stage during the 2022 Academy Awards ceremony. This is false; the images are from 2017, when \"La La Land\" was mistakenly announced instead of \"Moonlight\" as the winner of the Oscar for Best Picture.", "author": "AFP", "date": "31 March 2022 7:38 AM GMT", "image_set1": ["https://www.boomlive.in/h-upload/2022/03/31/973691-untitled-design-54.webp"], "image_set2": []}
{"source_url": "https://www.boomlive.in/world/2014-riots-kyiv-ukraine-russian-invasion-17350", "article_heading": "Images From 2014 Used To Compare Kyiv Before And After Russian Invasion", "short_context": "On February 25, 2022, a Facebook post shared two images of Maidan Nezalezhnosti, the central square of Kyiv also known as Independence Square.", "short_into": "Facebook posts with contrasting aerial images showing Ukraine's capital Kyiv both untouched by war and in ruins have been shared hundreds of times with the claim that the pictures show the city before and after Russia's invasion. The claim is misleading; while the first image of the city intact is fresh, the second showing devastation in the capital was taken about eight years ago during deadly protests that ushered in a change of government.", "author": "AFP", "date": "31 March 2022 8:39 AM GMT", "image_set1": ["https://www.boomlive.in/h-upload/2022/03/31/973699-russia-03.webp"], "image_set2": []}
{"source_url": "https://www.boomlive.in/world/joe-biden-europe-visit-white-house-fact-check-fake-news-17351", "article_heading": "Was Joe Biden's Image Before Europe Departure Staged? Truth About Viral Photo", "short_context": "Posts claimed the image was staged because it showed leaves on trees while most vegetation in the nation's capital was still bare-branched.", "short_into": "Social media posts suggest an official photo of US President Joe Biden's departure for Europe in late March 2022 was staged because it showed leaves on trees while most vegetation in the nation's capital was still bare-branched. This is false; the photo is authentic and the trees are southern magnolias, which retain their leaves throughout the year.", "author": "AFP", "date": "31 March 2022 9:58 AM GMT", "image_set1": ["https://www.boomlive.in/h-upload/2022/03/31/973716-untitled-design-55.webp"], "image_set2": []}
{"source_url": "https://www.boomlive.in/world/malaysian-health-authorities-fourth-covid-19-vaccine-fact-check-17353", "article_heading": "Did Malaysian Authorities Ask Citizens To Get Fourth Covid-19 Jab?", "short_context": "As of March 25, 2022, the government had not issued any statement about plans for the fourth dose in the country.", "short_into": "An infographic purportedly issued by Malaysian health authorities has been shared multiple times on social media with a claim that residents should get a fourth dose of the Covid-19 vaccine because \"the Omicron variant will spread\" after Malaysia reopens borders on April 1, 2022. However, the claim is false; the Malaysian Ministry of Health denies issuing the infographic. As of March 25, 2022, the government has not issued any statement about plans for the fourth dose in the country. ", "author": "AFP", "date": "31 March 2022 10:10 AM GMT", "image_set1": ["https://www.boomlive.in/h-upload/2021/12/13/965206-covid-19-omicron-vaccine-booster-shot.webp"], "image_set2": []}
{"source_url": "https://www.boomlive.in/world/fake-cnn-tweet-hotel-ukraine-russia-fake-news-fact-check-17359", "article_heading": "Fake CNN Tweet Shared To Show Attack On Hotel Of A Journalist In Ukraine", "short_context": "The screenshot of the doctored tweet features the social media handle of a prankster who has previously shared fake CNN tweets.", "short_into": "Multiple social media posts claim CNN fabricated a story about a \"bomb attack\" at the hotel of a journalist in Ukraine in a tweet that actually showed an old photo of a hotel in Serbia. However, CNN reported no such story and said the tweet was fake. The screenshot of the doctored tweet features the social media handle of a prankster who has previously shared fake CNN tweets.", "author": "AFP", "date": "31 March 2022 11:41 AM GMT", "image_set1": ["https://www.boomlive.in/h-upload/2022/03/31/973735-untitled-design-56.webp"], "image_set2": []}
{"source_url": "https://www.boomlive.in/world/french-film-russian-attack-eiffel-tower-fake-news-fact-check-17358", "article_heading": "Clip From French Film Shared As Russian Attack On 'Eiffel Tower'", "short_context": "The footage shows a fictional film created by a French director that was then shared online by Ukrainian officials in a bid to urge European authorities to impose a no-fly zone over Ukraine.", "short_into": "A video that appears to show explosions in the French capital of Paris has been viewed thousands of times in misleading social media posts that claim it shows a real attack on the Eiffel Tower. The posts suggest the attack was carried out by Russian forces in response to sanctions from foreign powers following its invasion of neighbouring Ukraine. The footage, however, has been shared in a false context: it shows a fictional film created by a French director that was then shared online by Ukrainian officials in a bid to urge European authorities to impose a no-fly zone over Ukraine.", "author": "AFP", "date": "31 March 2022 11:30 AM GMT", "image_set1": ["https://www.boomlive.in/h-upload/2022/03/31/973734-eiffel-tower-7201.webp"], "image_set2": []}
{"source_url": "https://www.boomlive.in/world/canadian-sniper-wali-russia-ukraine-fake-news-fact-check-17361", "article_heading": "No, Canadian Sniper 'Wali' Wasn't Killed While Fighting Russia In Ukraine", "short_context": "Wali, a former Canadian Armed Forces sniper, dispelled the rumours of his death during a video call from Ukraine.", "short_into": "Multiple posts on Facebook have claimed that a sharpshooting Canadian sniper known as Wali was killed by Russian special forces 20 minutes after he arrived on the frontline in Mariupol, Ukraine as a volunteer fighter. However, this is false; the man, a former Canadian Armed Forces sniper, dispelled the rumours of his death during a video call from Ukraine where he continues to fight Russia's invading troops. ", "author": "AFP", "date": "31 March 2022 11:48 AM GMT", "image_set1": ["https://www.boomlive.in/h-upload/2022/03/31/973740-untitled-design-57.webp"], "image_set2": []}
